      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Robert Pope</b>\n</p><p><b>Robert Pope</b>,<br />\nan American computer chess programmer, and author of the <a href=\"/WinBoard\" title=\"WinBoard\">WinBoard</a> compliant chess engines <a href=\"/Beaches\" title=\"Beaches\">Beaches</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>, an <a href=\"/Category:Open_Source\" title=\"Category:Open Source\">open source engine</a> of a mixed <a href=\"/Bitboards\" title=\"Bitboards\">bitboard</a> with <a href=\"/Mailbox\" title=\"Mailbox\">mailbox</a> approach, and more recently, <a href=\"/Abbess\" title=\"Abbess\">Abbess</a>, based on <a href=\"/Magic_Bitboards\" title=\"Magic Bitboards\">Magic Bitboards</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#1999\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1999</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2020_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2020 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Robert_Pope&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1999\">1999</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Robert_Pope&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 1999\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=56237\">Swiss Pairing question</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Robert Pope</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 16, 1999</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Robert_Pope&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=100213\">ECO question</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Robert Pope</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 04, 2000&#160;» <a href=\"/ECO\" title=\"ECO\">ECO</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=127509\">Number of reachable positions</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Robert Pope</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 30, 2000</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=217021\">Re: Hey, I do that!</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Robert Pope</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 08, 2002</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=4&amp;t=4641\">make/unmake</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Robert Pope</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, April 08, 2006</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=18163\">SEE algorithm</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Robert Pope</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 02, 2007&#160;» <a href=\"/Static_Exchange_Evaluation\" title=\"Static Exchange Evaluation\">Static Exchange Evaluation</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=27680\">0x88 engines</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Robert Pope</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 01, 2009</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Robert_Pope&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=19&amp;t=51142\">Multiple WinBoard installations</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Robert Pope</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, August 17, 2010&#160;» <a href=\"/WinBoard\" title=\"WinBoard\">WinBoard</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=48173\">0x88 with pointers</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Robert Pope</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 01, 2013</li></ul>\n<p><b>2015</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=55042\">Working with CLOP</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Robert Pope</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 22, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/CLOP\" title=\"CLOP\">CLOP</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=55301\">Initializing portions of arrays</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Robert Pope</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 12, 2015</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=56647\">value &gt; beta</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Robert Pope</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 10, 2015&#160;» bug in <a href=\"/CPW-Engine_search\" title=\"CPW-Engine search\">CPW-Engine_search</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=56830\">Alpha-Beta bug?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Robert Pope</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 30, 2015</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=57181\">Tapered Eval</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Robert Pope</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 05, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Tapered_Eval\" title=\"Tapered Eval\">Tapered Eval</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=57603\">Transposition table test positons</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Robert Pope</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 11, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=57713\">Beaches 1.20</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Robert Pope</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 21, 2015</li></ul>\n<p><b>2016</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=59304\">KnightCap source code</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Robert Pope</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 19, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/KnightCap\" title=\"KnightCap\">KnightCap</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=62053\">TD-leaf(lambda)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Robert Pope</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 09, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Temporal_Difference_Learning#TDLeaf\" title=\"Temporal Difference Learning\">TDLeaf(λ)</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=62528\">Abbess 2016</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Robert Pope</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 19, 2016</li></ul>\n<p><b>2017</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=63287\">Opening book trees</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Robert Pope</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 27, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Opening_Book\" title=\"Opening Book\">Opening Book</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=63504\">Probing tablebases in python-chess</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Robert Pope</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 20, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Gaviota_Tablebases\" title=\"Gaviota Tablebases\">Gaviota Tablebases</a>, <a href=\"/Python-chess\" title=\"Python-chess\">python-chess</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2020_...\">2020 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Robert_Pope&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2020 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=73753\">Null move</a>  by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Robert Pope</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 24, 2020&#160;» <a href=\"/Null_Move_Pruning\" title=\"Null Move Pruning\">Null Move Pruning</a>, <a href=\"/Stockfish\" title=\"Stockfish\">Stockfish</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Robert_Pope&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://sites.google.com/site/abbesschess/\">Abbess Chess</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://sites.google.com/site/beacheschess/\">BeachesChess</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Robert_Pope&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://sites.google.com/site/beacheschess/\">BeachesChess</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=62528\">Abbess 2016</a> by <a class=\"mw-se